---
description: Reinstall after project changes
globs: find_artwork.py,find_tags.py,fix_album.py,music_common.py,menu_bar.py,install.sh,requirements.txt
alwaysApply: false
---

After editing `find_artwork.py`, `find_tags.py`, `menu_bar.py`, `install.sh`, or `requirements.txt`, run:

```bash
./install.sh
```

This refreshes the `music-artwork` CLI symlink and restarts the menu bar app.
